name: You Got Me Like Whoa Genesis
description:
KUMELA KUMSLUT, 2021

""You Got Me Like Whoa"" is a confrontation soundtrack to deal and heal from the heartbreak of an unrequited love. The continuation of 'Sünshine' - a good old friend of mine that I had a karmic relationship with. I wrote 'Yoü Got Me Like' to deal and heal from my heartbreak. This is my last song about him and it's about my struggles to accept the fact that I had to let go of him and all that we had. Letting go of the ones we Love deeply is never easy. But that doesn't mean we don't or kan't Love them for eternity. Even if the Love was just temporary, but we'll always have the good memories.

Please visit www.pinktank.art for more information.
